So a song like "We Are Family,"
which is basically just

01:01:42.954 --> 01:01:43.662
[PLAYING GUITAR].

01:01:50.090 --> 01:01:51.210
Right, the 11 chord?

01:01:57.830 --> 01:02:32.958
But that ain't-- the guitar
