01:02:32.958 --> 01:02:36.410
[APPLAUSE]

01:02:36.410 --> 01:02:39.540
See, that's fun to play.

01:02:39.540 --> 01:02:42.080
That is a hell of a lot
more fun to play than just,

01:02:42.080 --> 01:02:47.306
[PLAYING GUITAR], we are family.

01:02:47.306 --> 01:02:49.270
I got all my sisters.

01:02:49.270 --> 01:02:50.930
That's not fun.

01:02:50.930 --> 01:03:01.240
But [PLAYING GUITAR] that's fun.

